{"tid":2072594,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"8年前啲人唔俾錢買點樣睇成人動作片？","createTime":"2020-06-20T16:43:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-21T04:38:22.000Z","uid":112551,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"b569323bc032cd2685f127f133af2ced2027d430","tid":2072594,"uid":112551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T16:43:54.000Z","msg":"8年唔算長又唔算短，雨革下年都8周年，小弟都係8年前無師自通識打丁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n但個時要上網down or 睇 av真係好煩，舊少少既bt down成日/星期，網上av又唔齊又低resolution，得thisav個啲揀。<br />\n但慢慢有咗mega 又有 googledrive，又有 avgle 呢啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，見到時代既發展不禁令我感嘆世界既轉變，網上幾乎要搵咩片就有咩片。<br />\n但明明8年前我仲suffer緊低resolution 龜速 又唔齊片，好好奇以前啲人尤其學生，買唔到又想上網睇會係咩感受。<br />\n連登有無年紀大啲ching分享下 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"212bb319f4226a4f7713f7c44d17269b51a5ecc2","tid":2072594,"uid":241504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T16:56:24.000Z","msg":"三上岩出道好正"},{"pid":"addf6284084950fb4398f7af9254e344d8a4b513","tid":2072594,"uid":301989,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T16:59:59.000Z","msg":"雨革八年前？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ded1c8da66301d9716c069c38221c0f3fb53926","tid":2072594,"uid":105678,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T17:22:14.000Z","msg":"Foxy囉，依加啲00後<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa5bf090db423d4e94b6bb4f594cfdd9953c2208","tid":2072594,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"addf6284084950fb4398f7af9254e344d8a4b513","tid":2072594,"uid":301989,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T16:59:59.000Z","msg":"雨革八年前？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T17:22:40.000Z","msg":"00後數係咁上下"},{"pid":"e803e56bac7158b10c433181829205a52a2f8abd","tid":2072594,"uid":4